    "created_at": "2016-04-21T04:18:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-21T04:18:26Z",
    "body": "@baconface just an FYI but Node is completely removed from webviews which hosts remote content (dependent on webview attributes you specify) in our fork and we're hoping to upstream. It is also sandboxed which we also hope to upstream. We also hope to help with faster upgrades to major releases in the futrue. \n\nFor the amount we get for free by using Electron vs the amount patched, it was a very good idea for us.  I don't think we misunderstood or misused, but instead understood that some things needed to be adapted.  So we adapted to what we needed, which is also how Electron gets developed over time in general too.\n"
  },
