    "created_at": "2016-04-21T04:27:56Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-21T04:28:59Z",
    "body": "I appreciate the efforts Electron team has done. But it's the goal we're discussing here.  And security is not a half measure. It's fine if you are not able to deliver a big secure chunk of software due to limited resources, but at least developers and end users should be warned if they are at risk.\n"
